data.description: Your dream home awaits in the Tollgate Crossing neighborhood of Aurora. With 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a 2-car attached garage, a charming backyard patio, private yard, and cutting-edge radon mitigation system, this property is the epitome of modern living! 4767 S Elk Way is ideally situated, providing easy access to local shopping, dining, and recreational options. The neighborhood embodies a sense of community. The highly sought out community of Tollgate Crossings offers beautiful parks, and a neighborhood Clubhouse and pool. This home is conveniently located within walking distance of Cherry Creek schools and a Ninja Warrior Park! Schedule your showing today and come see for yourself what this property has to offer!
